<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>로그인</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      background: #f3f5fb;
      color: #1f2937;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Malgun Gothic", sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .login-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 32px;
      max-width: 380px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .login-card h1 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .login-card .lead {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .btn-brand {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      color: #fff;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .btn-brand:hover { color: #fff; opacity: 0.92; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-card">
    <h1><i class="bi bi-key me-2"></i>로그인</h1>
    <div class="lead">
      비공개 사이트입니다. 접근 비밀번호를 입력해 주세요.
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-danger small"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="post" action="/login">
      <input type="hidden" name="next" value="<%= next %>" />
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label small fw-semibold">비밀번호</label>
        <div class="input-group">
          <input type="password" name="password" id="pwInput" class="form-control" required autofocus autocomplete="current-password" />
          <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" id="pwToggle" tabindex="-1" aria-label="비밀번호 보기/숨기기">
            <i class="bi bi-eye" id="pwIcon"></i>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="form-text small text-secondary mt-1" style="font-size: 0.74rem;">
          한글 비밀번호 사용 시 한영 전환과 띄어쓰기에 주의하세요.
        </div>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-brand w-100">
        <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-1"></i>입장
      </button>
    </form>

    <script>
      (function() {
        var input = document.getElementById('pwInput');
        var btn   = document.getElementById('pwToggle');
        var icon  = document.getElementById('pwIcon');
        if (!input || !btn || !icon) return;
        btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
          var shown = input.type === 'text';
          input.type = shown ? 'password' : 'text';
          icon.className = shown ? 'bi bi-eye' : 'bi bi-eye-slash';
          input.focus();
        });
      })();
    </script>

    <div class="text-secondary small mt-4 pt-3 border-top" style="font-size: 0.78rem;">
      ※ 비밀번호는 30일간 이 브라우저에 기억됩니다.
      구독 해제 메일 링크는 비밀번호 없이 동작합니다.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
